<li id="cite_note-14"><b><a href="#cite_ref-14" title="">^</a></b> Fest, <i>The Face of the Third Reich</i>, 89. These sentiments were reciprocated by some on the <a href="/wiki/Left-wing" title="Left-wing" class="mw-redirect">left</a>. Richard F. Hamilton, <i>Who Voted for Hitler?</i>, Princeton University Press 1982, 570 quotes strikingly anti-Semitic statements made by some German Communist leaders in their efforts to create a common front between Communist and National Socialist workers.</li>
