<li id="cite_note-93"><b><a href="#cite_ref-93" title="">^</a></b> Vinogradov, <i>Hitler's Death</i>, 34</li>
<li id="cite_note-94"><b><a href="#cite_ref-94" title="">^</a></b> Fest, <i>The Face of the Third Reich</i>, 97</li>
</ol>
